# 📝 Practice Assignments
✅ Assignment 1: Banking System Database

Tables:

Customers (CustomerID, Name, Address, Phone)

Accounts (AccountID, CustomerID, Balance, Branch)

Transactions (TransactionID, AccountID, Amount, TransactionType, Date)

Write queries:

Insert new customers and accounts

Transfer money between accounts

Show account statement of customer

✅ Assignment 2: Student Management Database

Tables:

Students (StudentID, Name, Age, DepartmentID)

Departments (DepartmentID, DepartmentName)

Courses (CourseID, CourseName)

Enrollments (StudentID, CourseID)

Tasks:

Find all students enrolled in "Data Science"

Count students in each department

Insert enrollment records

✅ Assignment 3: Inventory Management System

Tables:

Products (ProductID, ProductName, Price, QuantityInStock)

Suppliers (SupplierID, SupplierName, City)

Orders (OrderID, SupplierID, OrderDate)

OrderDetails (OrderDetailID, OrderID, ProductID, QuantityOrdered)

Tasks:

List products low in stock (Quantity < 10)

Insert new order with products

Show total sales per product
